{"id":71922,"date":[{"year":1939,"month":5,"day":7}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"儿童园","column":"诗歌","genre":"文学作品","count":"211","ytitle":"","mtitle":"祖国不会亡","ftitle":"","authors":["思秋"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"思秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯火昏黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已闯进了梦之乡:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦见祖国变了一只船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大海中漂荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我正在恐慌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然船里的乘客们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐起来帮忙:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的把着舵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的打着桨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲过了狂风大浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我醒来了，我仔细的想:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国一定不会亡!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯火昏黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已闯进了梦之乡:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦见祖国变了一株树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枯萎得没有一些生气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我正在徬徨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然树上吹过一阵春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芽儿又缀满在枝上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一霎时抽成叶儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一霎时花儿也开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回复了欣欣向荣的模样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我醒来了，我仔细的想:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国一定不会亡!"}]}